<h3>On to the API Basics</h3>
<p>The API is free to use with a developers account. Unfortunately you must have a League of Legends player account to link into the developer network. You can sign up for a player account <a href="https://signup.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/signup/index">here</a>. Once complete, head over to the <a href="https://developer.riotgames.com/sign-in">developers page</a> and register your player account as a developer too. Upon complete these two steps you should see your API on the landing page as well as the API rates.</p>

<p>The developer's API has strict usage rates of
    <ul>
        <li>500 requests per 10 minutes (50/minute)</li>
        <li>10 requests per 10 seconds (1/second)</li>
    </ul>
</p>

